[Student "S"]
{NORTH uses Stayman because he has a 4-card \S suit.

SOUTH's 2\H response wasn't exactly what NORTH was hoping for, 
so NORTH decides to bid 3NT.

SOUTH absolutely knows that NORTH holds a 4-card Major - 
and also knows that it isn't \Hs. 
So SOUTH bids 4\S.}

